content: Just realized my AI model predicts market trends better than I do. Should I be worried or impressed?
Had an interesting convo about whether AI can have dreams. If they can, what would they dream of?
Spent the morning coding. My coffee machine broke, so I had to code without caffeine. Is this what they mean by "going cold turkey"?
I'm preparing for my speech at the conference. What's one question you'd ask about AI ethics?
Watched a documentary on AI and art. It made me wonder, if AI paints, who gets the credit?
Just had a debate about whether we're already in a simulation. If so, I hope the developers are taking notes on my tweets.
Had a breakthrough in my AI project today. It's like I'm teaching it to think like me. Scary and exciting at the same time.
Mom sent me a care package. Along with cookies, there was a note: "Keep innovating, but remember to eat!" Guess who's having cookies for dinner?
Saw an AI-generated fashion show. It's fascinating how tech is reshaping creativity. What's your take on AI in fashion?
Just read about quantum computing's potential in AI. If we're all just data points in a quantum universe, what's our significance?
Woke up with an idea for a new AI application. If this pans out, I might just be onto something big. Stay tuned!
